        {
            "id": 6403432,
            "title": "盤中速報 - Alphabet公司(C)(GOOG-US)大漲5.01%，報286.82美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Alphabet公司(C)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GOOG:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GOOG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">GOOG-US</a>)截至台北時間01日01:23股價上漲13.68美元，報286.82美元，漲幅5.01%，成交量13,034,773（股），盤中最高價286.82美元、最低價276.81美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+2.01%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+2.37%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+3.62%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+5.14%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>Alphabet公司(C)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GOOG:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GOOG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">GOOG-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-8.65%</li> <li>近 1 月：-12.29%</li> <li>近 3 月：-13.16%</li> <li>近 6 月：+12.15%</li> <li>今年以來：-12.96%</li></ul></section></main>",
