            "title": "盤中速報 - Alphabet公司(A)(GOOGL-US)大漲5.01%，報287.2美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Alphabet公司(A)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GOOGL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GOOGL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">GOOGL-US</a>)截至台北時間01日01:15股價上漲13.7美元，報287.20美元，漲幅5.01%，成交量18,001,202（股），盤中最高價287.21美元、最低價277.09美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+2.1%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+2.51%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+3.53%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+4.95%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>Alphabet公司(A)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GOOGL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GOOGL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">GOOGL-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-9.46%</li> <li>近 1 月：-12.27%</li> <li>近 3 月：-12.86%</li> <li>近 6 月：+12.51%</li> <li>今年以來：-12.62%</li></ul></section></main>",
